"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-france-got-very-questionable-whistle-to-avoid-upset-loss-to-japan-mens-basketball-paris-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"France escaped a tight basketball matchup against Japan at the 2024 Paris Olympics on Tuesday, and the French got a lot of help from the officials to save them at the end.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999751168132018, \"rank\": 0.00024362707040810085, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5939186823590407, \"rank\": 0.6757337668782278, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 103, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9568441862628858, \"rank\": 0.025803760449315788, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan led 84-80 with 10 seconds left, when France's Rudy Gobert found Matthew Strazel on the perimeter.\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5939186823590407, \"rank\": 0.6757337668782278, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999751168132018, \"rank\": 0.00024362707040810085, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Gobert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rudy Gobert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Gobert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rudy_Gobert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Strazel pump-faked one defender, got a better angle and fired a three-pointer from the wing.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It went in, and officials whistled Japan's Yuki Kawamura for a foul.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5939186823590407, \"rank\": 0.6757337668782278, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 413, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_people\", \"score\": 0.9997443096734171, \"rank\": 0.00023153889306040936, \"text\": \"Yuki\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuki_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was just one problem, Kawamura did not appear to touch Strazel.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Video is below.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"france's 4 point play to stay alivepic.twitter.com/XooYz7FoT5  And this still photo seems to show there was no contact on the shot.\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 527, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999751168132018, \"rank\": 0.00024362707040810085, \"text\": \"france\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tough foul callpic.twitter.com/uRjj3cv9pH  Strazel made the free throw to tie the game 84-84.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kawamura missed a three-pointer at the other end and the game went to overtime.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France outlasted the Japanese to win 94-90 in the extra frame.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999751168132018, \"rank\": 0.00024362707040810085, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.994104349617433, \"rank\": 0.0031531890445084844, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the game, Japan's coach Tom Hovassedidn't dispute the call.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5939186823590407, \"rank\": 0.67573376